snippet.title: Legends Of Old v0.3 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey Guys! Legends Of Old v.0.3 has been released, which introduces the City of Thalanos as well as a new playable class, the Paladin! 

The entire game has undergone a major overhaul with regards to balance, itemization, and immersion thanks to the continuous feedback of our discord community. Thank you guys so much!

Legends Of Old is a free to play game that is funded entirely by donations. If you like what you see, please consider supporting us! 

Website!
https://www.legendsofold.net/

Discord!
https://discord.gg/hHjQwhz7KQ

Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/SupportLegendsOfOld

Paypal!
